<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khamhbawi laksawng a tampi kha Ruah bantukin a sur ko, Vawlei car kha
 a hrin tikah Keimah zong ka surhter tuah.

[C1]
   Keimah zong, keimah zong, keimah zong ka surter tuah. 2. Pathian ka
   Pa, ka lanhtak hlah, Keimah lung kha tawi hmanhseh; Dantat awk kha tlak
   hmanhning law, Keimah kha ka ruat rih ko.

[V2]
 A kan Khamhbawi ka lanhtak hlah, Nangmah sinah thuh ka duh, Na thachin
 hmuh ka duh tuk cang, Na duhnak bang ka ser ko.

[C2]
   Keimah zong, keimah zong, keimah zong ka surter tuah. 2. Pathian ka
   Pa, ka lanhtak hlah, Keimah lung kha tawi hmanhseh; Dantat awk kha tlak
   hmanhning law, Keimah kha ka ruat rih ko.

[V3]
 Maw Thlarau rak ka lanhtak hlah, Mitcaw mi khua hmuhter tuah, Jesuh
 thachin ka hmuhsak tuah, Keimah cungah rung ceu ko.

[C3]
   Keimah zong, keimah zong, keimah zong ka surter tuah. 2. Pathian ka
   Pa, ka lanhtak hlah, Keimah lung kha tawi hmanhseh; Dantat awk kha tlak
   hmanhning law, Keimah kha ka ruat rih ko.</lyrics>
<title>KEIMAH ZONG CH305</title>
</song>